description.p:
ENTITY Time_offset;
hour_offset : INTEGER;
minute_offset : OPTIONAL INTEGER;
sense : offset_orientation;
DERIVE
actual_minute_offset: INTEGER := NVL(minute_offset,0);
WHERE
WR1: { 0 <= hour_offset < 24 };
WR2: { 0 <= minute_offset <= 59 };
WR3: NOT (((hour_offset <> 0) OR (actual_minute_offset <>0))
AND (sense = exact));
END_ENTITY;
WR2 should relate to actual_minute_offset. Minute_offset may not be set!

